00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:04,100
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream")

3
00:01:04,100 --> 00:01:05,460
(Author: Lan Jiujiu)

4
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 2=

5
00:01:10,350 --> 00:01:11,080
You shouldn't look

6
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:12,700
at what you shouldn't
be looking at, Young Lady.

7
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:13,720
Stand still.

8
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:14,520
Don't move.

9
00:01:20,160 --> 00:01:22,120
The person coming should be
a Lady of Gentleness.

10
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:24,800
How do you know
it's a Lady of Gentleness?

11
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,720
By the sound.

12
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:29,880
The jade worn by a Lady of Gentleness

13
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:31,560
comes from Dongjiang.

14
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:33,160
The sound is slightly dull,

15
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:34,440
unlike top-quality jade.

16
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:37,440
You are a Lady of Gentleness too?

17
00:01:39,510 --> 00:01:40,200
Senior Attendant.

18
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:45,280
A mere Senior Attendant

19
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:49,320
actually dares to dream of
competing for the Emperor's bed.

20
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,920
Success depends on effort.

21
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:54,920
Perhaps His Majesty likes my type.

22
00:01:57,380 --> 00:01:59,980
It's thanks to Father's plea
that I was titled Lady of Gentleness.

23
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:02,760
I must seize the time to get a chance
to attend to him tonight.

24
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,600
Applying the juice
of this flower to your skin

25
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,760
can make it as supple as jade.

26
00:02:10,920 --> 00:02:12,160
Its fragrance is exquisite,

27
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,000
and

28
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,760
it has aphrodisiac effects.

29
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,000
It can make a man

30
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,280
unable to stop,

31
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:19,040
lost in ecstasy.

32
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,560
Is it that effective?

33
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,240
Absolutely.

34
00:02:22,610 --> 00:02:23,560
Then, pick more of them.

35
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:25,840
Attendant Li,

36
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:27,080
do you know

37
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,200
what flower this is?

38
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:29,840
Shady tricks.

39
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:31,800
Of course, I wouldn't know.

40
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,720
Women who enter the palace

41
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,480
must fight for favor.

42
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:37,040
So what if it's a shady trick?

43
00:02:37,340 --> 00:02:38,320
After all, in the palace,

44
00:02:38,330 --> 00:02:40,350
there's only one man available,
who is the Emperor.

45
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,520
Vulgar.

46
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,040
You're a seller of the art of seduction,

47
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,600
yet you think I'm vulgar?

48
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,240
Besides, it's you men

49
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,600
who liked vulgarity first.

50
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,200
Who?

51
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,120
Who's there?

52
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,360
Do you know who I am?

53
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:11,080
I am Senior Attendant Rou,
personally titled by the Emperor.

54
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,800
If you dare to scare me,

55
00:03:12,810 --> 00:03:14,400
I'll have His Majesty cut off your head!

56
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,720
We're stopping the search.

57
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,480
Go back.

58
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:23,550
Hurry, let's go.

59
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,680
It seems Lady Xu

60
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,040
is not as stupid as outsiders say.

61
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:33,120
She's quite good at framing others.

62
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,400
Let's go.

63
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,200
I'll see you out.

64
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,360
Keep walking straight,

65
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,580
and you will reach
the small gate out of the courtyard.

66
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,560
After you go out,

67
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:00,800
then take off the blindfold.

68
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,160
But I can't see.

69
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:03,560
How can I walk?

70
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,240
There are no obstacles ahead.

71
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,200
So, walk with confidence.

72
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,080
(I want to see)

73
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:29,640
(if you are truly foolish
or just pretending.)

74
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,240
(This is the scent of lake water.)

75
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,520
(Is he trying to silence me?)

76
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,760
(Or is he)

77
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,200
(testing me?)

78
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,120
At the hour of Zi tomorrow night,

79
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,480
see you at the Yuehui Pavilion.

80
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,240
I won't wait if you're late.

81
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:07,390
She caught Your Majesty
entering the garden at night.

82
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,520
There will be trouble.

83
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,040
It seems we can only kill her.

84
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,400
She doesn't recognize me.

85
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,880
This woman is strange.

86
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,520
I want to see

87
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:21,560
how she learns
the art of seduction from me.

88
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:22,880
Yes, Your Majesty.

89
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,000
Madam.

90
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:27,680
Madam.

91
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:28,360
Well?

92
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:30,380
Did you see clearly
who was hiding in the shadows?

93
00:05:30,420 --> 00:05:31,520
It was Senior Attendant Rou.

94
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,960
How could it be her?

95
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,680
And I used her name.

96
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,080
What a wench.

97
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:39,120
She must have been hiding to set me up.

98
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:43,240
Then, we'll strike first
to gain the upper hand.

99
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,640
Have you heard?

100
00:05:49,650 --> 00:05:51,520
Someone broke into
the Cold Palace last night.

101
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,840
If it were the Empress

102
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,460
in charge of the harem,
it would be fine.

103
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:56,600
But now,

104
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,760
it happens to be

105
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,960
the eccentric Lady Liu
of Bright Deportment.

106
00:06:00,190 --> 00:06:01,840
Someone accidentally disturbed her rest,

107
00:06:01,850 --> 00:06:03,120
and they almost lost their life.

108
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:05,360
Lady Liu of Gentleness, I misspoke.

109
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,680
It is fine.

110
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,360
But the one who
broke into the Cold Palace

111
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:11,520
is likely in big trouble today.

112
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,080
I know, right?

113
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,560
Today,

114
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,960
the person

115
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:19,400
will not escape death.

116
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:30,080
Greetings, Ladies.

117
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:36,720
(Broadly Learned and Determined)
Lady of Bright Deportment has arrived!

118
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:47,720
- Greetings, Your Ladyship.
- Greetings, Your Ladyship.

119
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:57,120
Be seated.

120
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:59,560
- Thank you, Your Ladyship.
- Thank you, Your Ladyship.

121
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,120
Her Ladyship asks

122
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:04,600
who went to the Cold Palace last night.

123
00:07:04,780 --> 00:07:06,480
Entering the Cold Palace
without permission

124
00:07:06,490 --> 00:07:07,880
is forbidden by His Majesty's rules.

125
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:10,320
Whoever dares to violate
the palace rules

126
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,200
is seeking death.

127
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,800
Will no one admit it?

128
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,080
Senior Attendant Rou,

129
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,240
you have a lot of nerve!

130
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,960
Your Majesty, someone sent
a secret report to Lady Liu

131
00:07:40,970 --> 00:07:42,470
stating Shen Zhinian
broke into the Cold Palace.

132
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,700
She is being interrogated
at Yurong Palace right now.

133
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,280
If she confesses to seeing Attendant Li,

134
00:07:46,380 --> 00:07:47,920
it will inevitably involve Your Majesty

135
00:07:48,110 --> 00:07:49,920
and cause suspicion
regarding the Cold Palace.

136
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,840
If she dares to mention me,

137
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:53,640
then

138
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,680
kill her.

139
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,120
This morning,

140
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,920
I heard from several maids on watch

141
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,320
that last night, someone
claiming to be Senior Attendant Rou

142
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:03,390
broke into the Cold Palace.

143
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:06,040
I was passing the Cold Palace
on my watch last night,

144
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:09,120
and I indeed heard a woman
claiming to be Senior Attendant Rou.

145
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,640
I heard it as well.

146
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,520
Shen Zhinian,

147
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,240
do you admit your guilt?

148
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,480
I did not go to
the Cold Palace last night.

149
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,560
I went to Lady Xu's palace.

150
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,240
You're slandering me.

151
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:21,800
How could you have come to my palace?

152
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,360
In the main hall,

153
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,280
because of my promotion

154
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:26,880
to Senior Attendant Rou,

155
00:08:27,100 --> 00:08:28,190
Lady Xu was very displeased.

156
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:30,200
I felt anxious at night

157
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,240
and could not sleep.

158
00:08:32,160 --> 00:08:33,800
So, I made some pastries myself

159
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:35,240
and went to Lady Xu's to apologize.

160
00:08:35,250 --> 00:08:36,490
Your Ladyship, please look into this.

161
00:08:36,500 --> 00:08:37,480
I saw with my own eyes...

162
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,920
I saw with my own eyes

163
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,480
the maids on watch say

164
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,720
it was Senior Attendant Rou

165
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,940
who broke into the Cold Palace.

166
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,240
Every bird leaves a trace.

167
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,680
If you went there,

168
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,800
I would find out.

169
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,600
Whoever is lying,

170
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:57,760
I will have her tongue ripped out.

171
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,080
Your Majesty,

172
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,600
Lady Liu wants to rip out
Senior Attendant Rou's tongue.

173
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,520
Oh?

174
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,840
In Lady Xu's palace,

175
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,440
there are several tuberose plants.

176
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:12,120
I am allergic to tuberose.

177
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,600
But to seek her forgiveness,

178
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,320
I had to wait at her palace gate.

179
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,160
The passing servants all saw me.

180
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,640
Tonight, Xu Baoqin

181
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,240
used my name at the Cold Palace.

182
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:26,720
I'm afraid there will
be trouble tomorrow.

183
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,920
Put on my cloak.

184
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:34,900
Go and return quickly.

185
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,680
Your Ladyship, please look.

186
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:50,800
She really did have
an allergic reaction.

187
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,400
Perhaps

188
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,040
you caught this somewhere else,

189
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,960
or you're allergic to something else?

190
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:55,960
Tuberose

191
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:58,360
was brought from home by Lady Xu.

192
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,880
In the entire palace,

193
00:09:59,890 --> 00:10:01,720
they are only found
at Lady Xu's palace gate.

194
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,980
If you do not believe me, Your Ladyship,

195
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,840
you can bring any other flower.

196
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:08,480
I can find out with one simple test.

197
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:10,320
I...

198
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:11,120
I...

199
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:14,640
You were upset because His Majesty
named me Senior Attendant Rou,

200
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:15,890
so you harassed me on the spot.

201
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,560
At night, you went to the garden

202
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:20,120
and shouted the title
"Senior Attendant Rou" on purpose.

203
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,960
You did it all just to frame me.

204
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:22,440
No.

205
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:22,760
I didn't...

206
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:24,580
Your waist pendant
was dropped in the Cold Palace.

207
00:10:25,690 --> 00:10:26,400
That's impossible.

208
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:28,680
I clearly double-checked
when I returned last night.

209
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,890
I didn't leave anything behind.

210
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,120
She really went there.

211
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,440
That's a serious crime.

212
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,880
How could she dare?

213
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:37,720
Your Ladyship.

214
00:10:37,730 --> 00:10:38,290
Your Ladyship.

215
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,800
Your Ladyship, please let me explain.

216
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,560
Your Ladyship.

217
00:10:40,570 --> 00:10:41,990
Your Ladyship, listen to my explanation.

218
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:42,640
Your Ladyship.

219
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,280
Your Ladyship.

220
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,320
Your Ladyship!

221
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,640
Xu Baoqin,

222
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,760
ten strokes of the cane

223
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,790
and one month of confinement
to serve as a warning to others.

224
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:04,120
So she is being punished.

225
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,320
As she should be.

226
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,240
Indeed.

227
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:13,000
An oral decree from the Dowager Consort.

228
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:23,240
For violating palace rules,

229
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,720
Lady Xu is stripped of her rank,

230
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,000
sentenced to tongue-removal,

231
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,920
and confined to the Cold Palace.

232
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:30,760
Can she even survive that?

233
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,200
Attendant Wu,

234
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,640
what is the meaning of this?

235
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,960
Bring her in.

236
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:41,480
Kneel.

237
00:11:45,090 --> 00:11:46,160
Your Ladyship, have mercy.

238
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:47,320
Your Ladyship, have mercy.

239
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:48,800
Who is this?

240
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:51,720
This is Jing, Lady Xu's maid.

241
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,080
She confessed

242
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:56,320
that Lady Xu broke into
the Cold Palace last night

243
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,560
to pick forbidden flowers.

244
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,120
Drag her away.

245
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:04,760
Your Ladyship...

246
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:05,920
Help me, Your Ladyship.

247
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:08,240
Your Ladyship, help me.

248
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,560
Save me.

249
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,240
This is so pitiable.

250
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,400
Your Ladyship!

251
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:18,600
All of you,
go out and watch her punishment.

252
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,160
Remember

253
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,560
to behave yourselves.

254
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:25,080
(Within these towering palace walls,)

255
00:12:25,400 --> 00:12:27,200
(one wrong step leads to eternal ruin.)

256
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,040
(If I want to survive,)

257
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:31,680
(I must secure the Emperor's
favor as soon as possible.)

258
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:46,620
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

259
00:12:48,340 --> 00:12:53,580
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

260
00:12:55,220 --> 00:12:57,580
♪If we don't meet♪

261
00:12:57,780 --> 00:13:01,020
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

262
00:13:01,220 --> 00:13:07,740
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

263
00:13:08,100 --> 00:13:14,540
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

264
00:13:14,900 --> 00:13:21,220
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

265
00:13:21,740 --> 00:13:28,420
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

266
00:13:28,420 --> 00:13:35,300
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

267
00:13:35,540 --> 00:13:41,420
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

268
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:48,940
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

269
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:55,780
♪Wanting to fold
my heart into a paper kite♪

270
00:13:56,060 --> 00:14:02,500
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

